
[train_ktp_yolo] No KTP_DATASET found and no --roboflow-key / ROBOFLOW_API_KEY provided.

Provide a YOLOv8-format KTP dataset and re-run, e.g.:
    set KTP_DATASET=C:\path\to\ktp-dataset
    backend\venv\Scripts\python.exe backend\scripts\train_ktp_yolo.py

Expected layout:
    <KTP_DATASET>/data.yaml
    <KTP_DATASET>/train/images/*.jpg
    <KTP_DATASET>/train/labels/*.txt
    <KTP_DATASET>/valid/images/*.jpg
    <KTP_DATASET>/valid/labels/*.txt

Easiest source: Roboflow Universe \u2192 search 'KTP Indonesia',
click Export, choose 'YOLOv8' format, and unzip locally.

